			<div class="post-3778 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-data-mining category-electronic-data category-personal-privacy tag-backblaze tag-big-data tag-bitcoin tag-bluffdale tag-digital-privacy tag-dropbox tag-financial-privacy tag-gnu-privacy-guard tag-mailvelope tag-spideroak tag-stellar-wind tag-tempest-attack tag-truecrypt tag-van-eck-phreaking tag-william-binney post_box top" id="post-3778">
